Warren Buffett ’s Berkshire Hathaway
Inc. hired Dan Fortin as senior vice president of the company’s
new commercial insurance unit.  Fortin joins from CNA Financial Corp., according to a
Business Wire statement today from Omaha, Nebraska-based
Berkshire’s specialty insurance unit.  To contact the reporter on this story:
